message.body: So this has been under the radar so dont mention it to your parents but My dad has to have a bypass... I'm just overwhelmed. Someone just asked me about my resolutions for 2012 and I couldn't even think about the future. I know this is intense for a text I just can't even get a word out if I tried.
I meant I started crying when they asked me about my resolutions out of fear. Fucked.
Oh martha!! We need to talk about this - text me tomorrow when you're free and I will call u from work
Ok, it'll proabably be in the afternoon
Text me! I will call u
